Function Enable-VMHostSSH
{
	
<#
.SYNOPSIS
	Enable SSH on all ESXi hosts in a cluster.
.DESCRIPTION
	This function enables SSH on all ESXi hosts in a cluster.
	It starts the TSM-SSH daemon and opens incoming TCP connections on port 22.
.PARAMETER Cluster
